---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="What to Expect">
  <section class="container-x py-14 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-center">What to Expect</h1>

    <!-- Slogan under heading -->
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-2xl text-center text-gray-700">
      Come. See. <span class="text-[#B3282D]">Jesus</span>
    </p>
  
    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">A diverse community</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Multiracial and multigenerational — you belong here.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Music, singing & dancing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We echo heaven's joy with music singing and dancing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">The Lord’s Table</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We gather at the Table to remember what Jesus did for us.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">See Jesus in the Bible</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Clear, gospel-rich teaching from the Bible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Extravagant generosity</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Made rich by what Jesus has done, we are generous and share in all things.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Go live the story</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We are then sent out to live the story of Jesus aloud in our city, nation and the world.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Kids Ministry (Coming Soon) -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-orange-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Kids @The Life Place</h3>
          <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-[#B3282D] px-2 py-0.5 text-m text-center font-semibold text-white">
            Coming Soon
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          At present there is no kids church. As Jesus supplies the resources needed, 
          we will launch one where our children too will <em>Come. See. Jesus.</em>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">
          Children are welcome to remain with their parents during service.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>